            <title>[PDFBOX-5654] Avoid NPE when processing CFF2 based fonts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5654</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5631&quot; title=&quot;Support version 0.5 of MaximumProfileTable&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5631&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5631&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; adds rendering support for CFF-based fonts. That support is limited to CFF based fonts. The newer CFF2 format isn&apos;t supported which may lead to a NPE while loading local fonts when creating the font cache.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
